codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Industrius es~, discipule! Semper magistrō pārē~! Choose from this set of possible answers [ tō tō, tōte tōte, tō itō, itōte, tō, tō, itō] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-002' where ANSWER in [ 'tō tō', 'tōte tōte', 'tō itō', 'itōte', 'tō', 'tō', 'itō']
